Class RobotProgram

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.RobotBase
      • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.IterativeRobotBase
        • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.TimedRobot
          • io.github.frc5024.lib5k.autonomous.RobotProgram
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public abstract class RobotProgram
extends TimedRobot
    RobotProgram is the base class for all robot programs. This contains tools for various operation modes. The command scheduler is run behind the scenes.
